(5, 11, NULL, 7, 'How to Setup a Bluetooth Printer on iPhone?', 'how-to-setup-a-bluetooth-printer-on-iphone', '/upload/blog/64d4ae0f13ca4how-to-setup-a-bluetooth-printer-on-iphone.webp', 'How to Setup a Bluetooth Printer on iPhone?', '<p dir=\"ltr\">A Bluetooth printer is suitable for good reasons. You can add this printer to your device and start to print seamlessly. Just one thing you need to make sure is to keep the printer and iPhone devices in the range. This blog post will discuss easy procedures to setup a Bluetooth printer on iPhone. It will help you pair the device and begin printing whatever you want.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">If you want to print without the hassles of wires, Bluetooth pairing is a good alternative. This wireless connectivity requires you to connect the printer to your device. Let&#39;s get into the complete process of setup.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">The Process to Connect a Bluetooth Printer to Your iPhone</h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">You can add your printer to your iPhone easily. After a proper connection, you can begin printing photos, documents, or whatever files you want. Here are a few instructions that you require to follow.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<li>First, confirm that you have charged the battery of your iPhone.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Connect the device to an AC outlet.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Next, confirm that you have loaded compatible receipt paper.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>After that, move to your printer and turn it on.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Now, jump into the steps to connect your device.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Move to iOS device Settings.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Click on Settings and then go to Bluetooth.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"https://support.apple.com/library/content/dam/edam/applecare/images/en_US/iOS/ios16-iphone13-pro-settings-general.png\"><img alt=\"How to Setup a Bluetooth Printer on iPhone\" src=\"https://bluetoothprintersetup.com/upload/medai/64d4acd08470cios16-iphone13-pro-settings-general.png\" style=\"height:1070px; width:590px\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<ul dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<li>Toggle the option and make the Bluetooth ON.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Now, set up a printer station.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Finally, the printer gets connected to an iPhone device.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">These are the steps explaining how you can pair the Bluetooth printer and your iPhone. However, if you fail to execute, contact a printer expert immediately. Ask for a free consultation by going to the Support page of <a href=\"http://bluetoothprintersetup.com\">bluetoothprintersetup.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>The Process to Print from Your iPhone Using Bluetooth&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Here is the simple process with step-by-step instructions to help you print documents with a Bluetooth printer. Printing from an iPhone device is as simple as printing from another device. Go through these steps to print the page or document you want to print from your handheld iPhone. Once you setup a Bluetooth printer on iPhone, you can start to print.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<li>Initiate by ensuring that your printer is discoverable.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Now, turn on Bluetooth on your device.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Go to the Settings tab on your device and choose the Bluetooth option.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Slide the button and make Bluetooth active on your device. You can see the B symbol next to your battery indicator.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/image16.png?w=620\"><img alt=\"Setup a Bluetooth Printer on iPhone\" src=\"https://bluetoothprintersetup.com/upload/medai/64d4acd08444aimage16.webp\" style=\"height:1102px; width:620px\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<ul dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<li>Once you switch on the Bluetooth, you will find a list of all the connected devices.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Click on the name of your printer. The portable device will then connect to your printer.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Later, move to the document you need to print.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Open the webpage, save the iBook or pages you have to print.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>You will get options for different actions when you click on the icon at the top of a box.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Find the Print icon by scrolling across the bottom line.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"https://i.insider.com/6390af038580f70019f7d338?width=750&amp;format=jpeg&amp;auto=webp\"><img alt=\"Bluetooth Setup Printer on iPhone\" src=\"https://bluetoothprintersetup.com/upload/medai/64d4acd083e7c6390af038580f70019f7d338.webp\" style=\"height:1291px; width:750px\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<p dir=\"ltr\">Click on it&nbsp;then, to print.&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">Why isn&#39;t the iPhone Supporting Printing via Bluetooth?&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Sometimes, printing from an iPhone gets complicated. Bluetooth is a great way to print from the device, but sometimes the situation fails. It can be because the Bluetooth isn&#39;t turned on. Or the device is not in the range. However, Bluetooth is not only a restriction. In this case, you can go for the AirPrint option. The iPhone supports AirPrint technology, enabling users to print from their devices. Also, if your printer doesn&#39;t support AirPrint, you can use Wi-Fi. Use a suitable app and ensure it is compatible with the make and model of your device.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">For more, you can take help from a skilful printer professional. They will provide a free consultation to connect the printer and resolve other issues. Visit our Support page through the link <a href=\"http://bluetoothprintersetup.com\">bluetoothprintersetup.com</a> and ask an expert for a free consultation.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">Conclusion&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The Bluetooth printer has been introduced in the market with many valuable features and functions. People prefer it because of the wireless features that it delivers. Bluetooth is the best option if you are an Iphone user and want to print something from your device. Learn to setup a Bluetooth printer on iPhone and print the document you need.&nbsp;</p>', 'How to Setup a Bluetooth Printer on iPhone?', 'Setup a Bluetooth Printer on iPhone', 'Learn an easy way to set up a Bluetooth printer on iPhone. This blog curates easy step-by-step instructions to connect the printer and print from iOS devices.', '0', '0', 1, '2023-08-10 03:59:51', '2023-08-10 07:52:58'),
(6, 11, NULL, 7, 'How to Connect Bluetooth Printer to Laptop?', 'how-to-connect-bluetooth-printer-to-laptop', '/upload/blog/64d4b39146e7fhow-to-connect-bluetooth-printer-to-laptop-1.webp', 'How to Connect Bluetooth Printer to Laptop?', '<p dir=\"ltr\">Did you get a brand-new Bluetooth printer? No matter what the brand and model of your printer is, you need to connect it to your device. After all, this will help your printer print from a laptop or any device in the range. But what when you are not tech-savvy? Luckily, we have a helpful guide for you. This write-up will help you quickly connect Bluetooth printer to laptop.</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">A Bluetooth printer works by connecting to devices that are in the range. So, if you want to print from your Windows or Mac laptop, have a walkthrough of this guide. Here, you will get to know easy steps for a successful connection.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">How to Connect Bluetooth Printer to Your Windows Laptop?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">When you plan to add a Bluetooth printer to a Windows laptop, you must go the same way as other devices. Ensure that the communication or COM port on Windows is the same as that of the printer driver. And then follow the steps below:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<li>First, go to the Start menu.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Click on the Settings/Gear option to open the Windows Setting.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"https://static.javatpoint.com/tutorial/windows/images/how-to-add-a-bluetooth-printer-to-windows-10-pc.png\"><img alt=\"Connect Bluetooth Printer to Laptop\" src=\"https://bluetoothprintersetup.com/upload/medai/64d4b21a0cd59how-to-add-a-bluetooth-printer-to-windows-10-pc.png\" style=\"height:506px; width:372px\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<ul dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<li>Once you click on the Setting option, a new window will display.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Hit on the Devices option.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"https://static.javatpoint.com/tutorial/windows/images/how-to-add-a-bluetooth-printer-to-windows-10-pc2.png\"><img alt=\"How to Bluetooth Printer to Connect Laptop \" src=\"https://bluetoothprintersetup.com/upload/medai/64d4b21a0cae5how-to-add-a-bluetooth-printer-to-windows-10-pc2.png\" style=\"height:503px; width:686px\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<ul dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<li>A new popup window will come when you tap on the Devices option.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Now, hit on Bluetooth and Other Devices.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>After that, click on the Bluetooth and other device option in the left sidebar.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Move to the Add Bluetooth or other device option.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Now, toggle the Bluetooth button and set it to ON.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"https://static.javatpoint.com/tutorial/windows/images/how-to-add-a-bluetooth-printer-to-windows-10-pc4.png\"><img alt=\"How to Connect Bluetooth Printer to Your Windows Laptop\" src=\"https://bluetoothprintersetup.com/upload/medai/64d4b21a0c48ahow-to-add-a-bluetooth-printer-to-windows-10-pc4.png\" style=\"height:643px; width:764px\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<ul dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<li>When you hit the Add Bluetooth or other device option, a new popup window will appear.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>You will get three additional options on the new popup window - Bluetooth, Wireless display, etc.</li>\r\n	<li>Choose the Bluetooth option to add your device.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Then, you will see the list of all detected Bluetooth devices.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Windows will search for the Bluetooth printer. Ensure to turn on your device.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"https://static.javatpoint.com/tutorial/windows/images/how-to-add-a-bluetooth-printer-to-windows-10-pc6.png\"><img alt=\"Connect Bluetooth Printer to Your Windows Laptop\" src=\"https://bluetoothprintersetup.com/upload/medai/64d4b21a0c291how-to-add-a-bluetooth-printer-to-windows-10-pc6.png\" style=\"height:254px; width:544px\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<ul dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<li>Select the Bluetooth print from the searched list.</li>\r\n	<li>After that, tap on the Ready button to start pairing.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Type in the PIN for your printer.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Otherwise, click on the Connect button.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Next, check the COM Port in Device Manager and install the printer driver via the same COM port.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Go to Control Panel &gt; Hardware and Sound and then Devices and Printers.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Connect To Printer Your Windows Laptop?\" src=\"https://bluetoothprintersetup.com/upload/medai/64d4b21a0c04fhow-to-add-a-bluetooth-printer-to-windows-10-pc7.png\" style=\"height:427px; width:787px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<ul dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<li>Then, right-click on the Bluetooth printer and choose Properties.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Execute all the on-screen directions to install the driver on your Windows laptop.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>At last, try to print a test page.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">When connecting your printer to a Windows laptop, you should use the same port to set the print driver to Windows Device Manager. If you face any issues, you can connect with printer experts by going to the Support page of <a href=\"http://bluetoothprintersetup.com\">bluetoothprintersetup.com</a>. They provide free consultation to resolve the issue.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">How to Connect Bluetooth Printer to Your Mac Laptop?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Do you want to print something from your Mac computer? Here are some easy guidelines that you can follow.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<li>First, go to the Apple menu on your Mac laptop.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Next, click on the System Preferences option.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"https://www.howtogeek.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/2-mac-system-preferences.png?trim=1,1&amp;bg-color=000&amp;pad=1,1\"><img alt=\"How to Connect Bluetooth Printer to Your Mac Laptop?\" src=\"https://bluetoothprintersetup.com/upload/medai/64d4b21a0bc9d2-mac-system-preferences.png\" style=\"height:485px; width:650px\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<ul dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<li>In the subsequent step, select Software Update and install all the listed software updates.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Now, confirm that your printer is ready for Bluetooth connection. You can use the instruction manual.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>After that, move again to the Apple menu and navigate to System Preferences.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Choose the Printers and Scanners option, then.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"https://60a99bedadae98078522-a9b6cded92292ef3bace063619038eb1.ssl.cf2.rackcdn.com/11324Image3.jpg\"><img alt=\"Connect Bluetooth Printer to Mac\" src=\"https://bluetoothprintersetup.com/upload/medai/64d4b21a0b6e711324image3.jpg\" style=\"height:325px; width:375px\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<ul dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<li>Later, hit on the Add button that is at the bottom.</li>\r\n	<li>Examine the list of printers and select your device.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Finally, select the Add option then.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">This is how you can connect Bluetooth printer to laptop. However, if you find any steps confusing, don&rsquo;t hesitate to ask for help. Connect with a proficient printer professional by visiting the support page of <a href=\"http://bluetoothprintersetup.com\">bluetoothprintersetup.com</a>. You can do a live chat or call to connect with them.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">Conclusion&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Printer users prefer a Bluetooth printer because of its convenience. The printer features an easy way to connect with several devices within the range. All you need is to learn how to connect Bluetooth printer to laptop. The process is effortless to execute. Once the connection establishes, you can print from your device without cables or wires.</p>', 'How to Connect Bluetooth Printer to Laptop?', 'Connect Bluetooth Printer to Laptop', 'Do you want to print from your Bluetooth printer? Learn how to connect Bluetooth printer to laptop. This blog talks about easy steps to connect the printer.', '0', '0', 1, '2023-08-10 04:23:21', '2023-08-10 05:07:17'),
