(11, 5, NULL, 7, 'Brother Bluetooth Printer Setup on Computer and Mobile Devices', 'brother-bluetooth-printer-setup-on-computer-and-mobile-devices', '/upload/blog/65001ce215e18bluetooth-printer-setup-blog-banners.webp', 'Brother Bluetooth Printer Setup on Computer and Mobile Devices', '<p><a href=\"https://bluetoothprintersetup.com/\"><strong>Brother printer</strong></a> has numerous printer types and models for printing, scanning, copying, and faxing functions. These printers work ideally for home, office, and business purposes. Moreover, the company provides its users with Bluetooth printers that support printing from computers and mobile devices without wires.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With a Bluetooth-connected printer, you don&#39;t have to plug your mobile phone into a computer or dock. Connect your printer to Bluetooth, ensuring it is in the range. This <strong><a href=\"https://bluetoothprintersetup.com/brother/brother-bluetooth-printer-setup-on-computer-and-mobile-devices\">Brother Bluetooth printer setup</a> </strong>post provides a straightforward process of connecting the printer to a computer and mobile device. Thus, get into it and make your printer ready to print wirelessly.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>How to Connect Brother Bluetooth Printer to a Windows Computer?</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Do you want to print from your printer via a Bluetooth connection? Here are the steps you will be required to follow for the process.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Initially, go to the <strong>Start menu</strong>.</li>\r\n	<li>Now, move to <strong>Settings </strong>and then <strong>Devices</strong>.</li>\r\n	<li>After that, enter <strong>Bluetooth and other devices</strong>.</li>\r\n	<li>Choose Bluetooth and then select your printer to complete the pairing process.</li>\r\n	<li>In the subsequent step, open <strong>Devices and Printers. </strong></li>\r\n	<li>Now, right-click on your printer icon.</li>\r\n	<li>In the following step, select <strong>Properties</strong>.</li>\r\n	<li>After that, open the <strong>Service </strong>tab and write down the port name. (It is at the right of the serial port SPP).</li>\r\n	<li>Now, utilize a USB cable to connect the computer and the printer.</li>\r\n	<li>You will then see a message - <strong>Device setup complete on the right of your screen.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong></li>\r\n	<li>Next, a printer icon will appear in the <strong>Devices and Printers</strong> option.</li>\r\n	<li>Right-click on your <strong>Brother printer</strong> icon and choose <strong>Printer Properties.</strong></li>\r\n	<li>Then, open the tab - <strong>Port </strong>and choose the port name you noted before.</li>\r\n	<li>Now, tap on <strong>OK</strong> and close the properties dialog box.</li>\r\n	<li>Lastly, close the printer&#39;s Windows to finish the process.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>You can implement simple instructions to connect a Brother printer to a computer using Bluetooth. But, if you are unable, you can go to this page <a href=\"https://bluetoothprintersetup.com/support\"><strong>support</strong></a> and connect with our printer professionals.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>How to Connect Brother Bluetooth Printer to a Mac Computer?</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Do you have a Mac with Bluetooth? And if you have a USB Bluetooth adapter, you can print easily to a Bluetooth-enabled Brother printer.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Initiate by going to your Mac device.</li>\r\n	<li>Now, update your printer&#39;s software if there are pending updates available.</li>\r\n	<li>Or, don&#39;t check for updates if there is an AirPrinter printer.</li>\r\n	<li>After that, unbox your printer and turn it on.</li>\r\n	<li>Follow the instructions to connect your primer via Bluetooth.</li>\r\n	<li>Then, start to add your printer to the printer&#39;s list.</li>\r\n	<li>Next, select the <strong>Apple menu </strong>and go to <strong>System Settings.</strong></li>\r\n	<li>In the next step, tap on <strong>Printers and Scanners</strong>.</li>\r\n	<li>Afterward, tap the <strong>Add Printer, Scanner, or Fax</strong> button and then the <strong>Default.</strong></li>\r\n	<li>Select your printer from the list and hit <strong>Add</strong> If you can&#39;t see your printer, type in your printer&#39;s model and then tap <strong>Return</strong>.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>After successfully following these steps, you must download the latest software. Download and install them for printing. For more details on <strong>Brother Bluetooth printer setup</strong>, you can visit <a href=\"http://bluetoothprintersetup.com/\"><strong>bluetoothprintersetup.com</strong></a>. Here, you can browse through easy instructions for a successful setup.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>How to Connect Brother Bluetooth Printer to a Mobile Device? </strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Here is a simple procedure to connect the printer to a mobile device. Make sure to follow these directions with caution.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Initially, power on your printer and enable Bluetooth. Make sure it is lit. If not, power on your printer and then press and hold the printer&#39;s <strong>Bluetooth</strong> button.</li>\r\n	<li>Now, please bring in your mobile device and use its display to show the list of all nearby devices.</li>\r\n	<li>In the case of <strong>Apple </strong>devices, click on <strong>Settings</strong> and then go to <strong>Bluetooth</strong>.</li>\r\n	<li>For <strong>Android</strong>, go to the phone&#39;s home screen, hit <strong>Settings</strong>, and <strong>toggle </strong>the button to enable <strong>Bluetooth</strong>.</li>\r\n	<li>Lastly, choose your Brother printer&#39;s model and enter the password.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Conclusion </strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Brother printer&#39;s Bluetooth model is capable of printing wirelessly. Users can follow easy procedures to connect the printer to a computer or phone and print. Printing becomes easy when there is a <a href=\"https://bluetoothprintersetup.com/brother/brother-bluetooth-printer-setup-on-computer-and-mobile-devices\"><strong>Brother Bluetooth printer setup</strong></a>. But, while connecting the printer with a <a href=\"https://bluetoothprintersetup.com/brother\"><strong>Bluetooth connection</strong></a>, ensure the printer and device are in the range.</p>', 'Brother Bluetooth Printer Setup on Computer and Mobile Devices', 'Brother Bluetooth Printer Setup, Brother Printer Setup, Brother Printer Guide', 'Are you looking for a straightforward process for Brother Bluetooth printer setup? This post discusses the process for computers and mobile devices.', '0', '0', 1, '2023-09-12 02:40:10', '2023-09-12 03:09:58'),
