(3, 'HP', 'hp', '/upload/category/64ccb01fbd8ebhp-bluetooth-printer-setup-for-windows-mac-android-ios.webp', 'HP Bluetooth Printer Setup', 'HP Bluetooth Printer Setup for Windows/Mac & Android/iOS', '<p dir=\"ltr\">Two types of wireless printers from HP include Bluetooth and Wi-Fi. Bluetooth printers from HP are easy to set up and use and are meant to be perfect for shops, offices, and other businesses. These printers use short-range wireless technology to print across several devices, from Windows and Mac computers to Android and iOS devices.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Here, we will discuss easy HP Bluetooth printer setup ways to help you use the printer on various devices. Have a walkthrough and set up your printer efficiently for smooth printing.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">How to Add HP Bluetooth Printer on Windows?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Bluetooth is an excellent option for wireless printing. If you want to print from your Windows computer, you must set up the connection and then begin printing. Here are step-by-step instructions to set up the printer on a Windows computer.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\">Step 1: Prepare Your HP Printer&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">First, connect your printer to a power outlet. Now, switch your printer on and turn on the printer&#39;s Bluetooth. Confirm the printer is discoverable.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\">Step 2: Move to Your Computer&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">After preparing the printer, move to your computer. After that, a few of the instructions you will need to follow are :&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<li>First, navigate to the computer&#39;s Bluetooth and tap on the search for nearby devices.&nbsp;<br />\r\n	<a href=\"https://support.content.office.net/en-us/media/3131018d-8ee2-4d70-b93d-2d6aed364789.png\"><img alt=\"HP Bluetooth Printer on Windows\" src=\"https://bluetoothprintersetup.com/upload/medai/64cba029696e03131018d-8ee2-4d70-b93d-2d6aed364789.png\" style=\"height:317px; width:558px\" /></a></li>\r\n	<li>The computer will then search and present the list of all nearby devices.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>After that, choose your printer model from the available list&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>At last, the computer will pair with your printing device.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\">Step 3: Install the Printer Drivers&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The last step of printer setup on Windows includes installing the printer drivers. You can use the CD or download the proper driver file from your printer&#39;s website. It will help you use your printer.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">These easy steps can help you set up your printer on a Windows computer. If some issues come your way, you can ask experts for a free consultation via call or live chat. Visit the <a href=\"https://bluetoothprintersetup.com/support\">Support page</a> and reach out to a printer professional.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">How to Add a Bluetooth-enabled HP Printer on Mac?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Macs with Bluetooth installed can print seamlessly to a Bluetooth HP printer. Here are some easy steps that they can carry to print through a Bluetooth connection.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Note: If you need a comprehensive guide on how to connect HP printer to Mac, then watch our video until the end<iframe frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/E25-iQ9S0zo?autoplay=1&amp;mute=1\" title=\"YouTube video player\" width=\"560\"></iframe></p>\r\n\r\n<ol dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<li>First, update printer software, i.e., drivers. In the case of an AirPrint printer, there is no need to perform software updates.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Then, turn on your printer and see if there are any errors.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>In the next step, follow all the instructions to connect your printer with Bluetooth.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Go through the steps below to add your Bluetooth printer to the printer list.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>After that, select the Apple menu and go to System Settings.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Tap on the Printers &amp; Scanners option that is in the sidebar.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Now, click on the Add Printer, Scanner, or Fax button.&nbsp;<br />\r\n	<a href=\"https://help.apple.com/assets/63BCA927AAE78C58DD7FBE35/63BCA92EAAE78C58DD7FBE76/en_GB/dfc2556ccad5a5cf4baf06723d60cfe7.png\"><img alt=\"Add a Bluetooth-enabled HP Printer on Mac\" src=\"https://bluetoothprintersetup.com/upload/medai/64cba0296adf1dfc2556ccad5a5cf4baf06723d60cfe7.png\" style=\"height:434px; width:666px\" /></a></li>\r\n	<li>Next, tap on the Default button.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Select your printer model from the available list of printers and tap on Add.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Alternatively, you can type in the name of your printer in the search field.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>In the following step, hit Return.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>When your printer connects to the Mac device, download and install the new software.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">If you can&#39;t find your printer in the list. Ensure you have the latest Bluetooth driver for the printer.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">How to Add a Bluetooth-enabled HP Printer to Android?&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Do you want a correct HP Bluetooth printer setup on an Android phone? Here are step-by-step instructions that you can execute.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<li>First of all, enable Bluetooth on your HP printer and Android phone.&nbsp;<br />\r\n	<img alt=\" Add a Bluetooth-enabled HP Printer to Android\" src=\"https://bluetoothprintersetup.com/upload/medai/64cba0296aa61android-bluetooth-2.webp\" style=\"height:648px; width:291px\" /></li>\r\n	<li>After that, move to the Settings menu on your smartphone.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Select the Bluetooth option, then.</li>\r\n	<li>Now, please tap on the Bluetooth switch and turn it on.</li>\r\n	<li>The Android device then starts scanning all the nearby Bluetooth devices.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Go to your printer from the list of devices and tap on it to pair.</li>\r\n	<li>Type in the passcode or PIN that is on the control panel of the printer or LCD screen.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Now, confirm the pairing with the Android device and the printer.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">After a successful pairing, your Android phone will show a confirmation message. You can print wirelessly from your device via Bluetooth with the above simple steps. However, if there are issues and you need expert help, contact a printer professional immediately. You can go to our <a href=\"https://bluetoothprintersetup.com/support\">Support page</a> for a free consultation.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">How to Add HP Bluetooth Printer to iOS Devices?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Printing from a Bluetooth-connected printer and iOS device is convenient with the simple steps below. Just follow them and get started with printing from your device.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Note: Are you looking for a video tutorial on how to connect HP printer to iPhone device? Then watch this.</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><iframe frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ykOPfalBbaI\" title=\"YouTube video player\" width=\"560\"></iframe></p>\r\n\r\n<ol dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<li>First, turn on the Bluetooth on your HP printer and iOS.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>After that, navigate to the Settings app and choose the Bluetooth option.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\"><img alt=\"add HP Bluetooth Printer to iOS Devices\" src=\"https://bluetoothprintersetup.com/upload/medai/64cb9f1be0a46epsonprinterviaandroid.png\" /></h2>\r\n\r\n<ol dir=\"ltr\" start=\"3\">\r\n	<li>If Bluetooth is not enabled, you must toggle the Bluetooth button.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>The iOS devices will then scan for all the nearby Bluetooth devices.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Next, locate your HP printer and tap on your printer model to start the pairing process.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>If there is a prompt, enter the passcode or PIN on the printer&#39;s LCD screen&#39;s control panel.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Finally, confirm the pairing with the HP printer and iOS device is successful.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">If you have no idea how to set up HP Bluetooth printer on Windows, Mac, Android, or iOS devices; follow the above steps. It will help you set up your printer and begin printing.&nbsp;</p>', 'HP Bluetooth Printer Setup for Windows/Mac & Android/iOS', 'HP Bluetooth Printer Setup', 'Discover easy steps for HP Bluetooth printer setup. This guide provides easy-to-follow directions for Windows, Mac, Android, and iOS devices.', 1, 0, '2023-06-13 04:42:31', '2023-08-05 03:53:04', '#0096d6'),
