(43, 5, 'Where is the Bluetooth Button on Brother Printer?', '<p>You can activate the Brother printer Bluetooth by following the steps shared in the pointers below:</p><ol><li>Tick the Menu button, and the Main Menu will get shared.&nbsp;</li><li>Use the upward or downward arrow, select Bluetooth &gt; On inside the Settings menu &gt; Press OK option.&nbsp;</li><li>With the help of the same arrows, choose Bluetooth &gt; Automatic Reconnection &gt; Press on under the Settings menu &gt; Tick OK box.&nbsp;</li><li>Press the back button to get connected to the main screen.&nbsp;</li><li>You will see the Bluetooth icon on the top right corner of the printer.&nbsp;</li></ol>', '2023-08-03 06:35:59', '2023-08-03 06:35:59'),
(44, 5, 'Why is My Brother Printer Not Connecting to My PC?', '<p>First, you must take the chance of disconnecting &amp; reconnecting the USB cable from both ends. Then, disconnect both your Brother printer &amp; PC. After that, try to reconnect it again. When the USB connection confirmation screen appears, press the Allow or Yes. (In case you are using a USB hub, remove it and directly connect your printer to the computer).<br></p>', '2023-08-03 06:35:59', '2023-08-03 06:35:59'),
(45, 5, 'Why is My Brother Printer Not Finding My PC?', '<p>Go through the following to learn about the process:</p><ul><li>Reboot your Desktop and switch on your Brother printer.</li><li>Reboot your router.</li><li>Attempt to scan from another network connected to your computer.</li><li>Wait for a few minutes till the scanning process comes to an end.&nbsp;</li></ul><p>The scanning will help you in seeing if your computer is causing any problems. The computer must be on the same network as the Brother printer.</p>', '2023-08-03 06:35:59', '2023-08-03 06:35:59'),
(46, 4, 'How Can I Add a Canon Bluetooth Printer to My Windows Computer?', '<p>Before adding the printer, you must pair the device to your computer. Below, we will show you how to add a printer to a Windows computer.&nbsp;</p><ol><li>First, go to the Start menu.&nbsp;</li><li>Move to Settings and then Bluetooth and other devices.&nbsp;</li><li>Now, click on Add Bluetooth or device.&nbsp;</li><li>After that, select Bluetooth to add.&nbsp;</li><li>Now, pair your computer and the printer.&nbsp;</li><li>In the following step, check the COM Port in Device Manager.&nbsp;</li><li>Start to install a print driver that matches the COM port.&nbsp;</li></ol><p>For any help, you can visit our Support page and contact a printer expert. We provide free consultation to all printer users.&nbsp;<br></p>', '2023-08-03 06:59:12', '2023-08-03 06:59:12'),
(47, 4, 'How to Connect the Canon Printer with Laptop Via Bluetooth?', '<p>A Bluetooth connection makes it easy to print from several devices. Below are the steps to connect the printer to a laptop to print several documents.&nbsp;</p><ol><li>Open the Control Panel on your laptop.&nbsp;</li><li>Now, go to the printers and devices options.&nbsp;</li><li>Next, click on the Bluetooth devices option and tap on Add Device.&nbsp;</li><li>The Bluetooth connection process will start.&nbsp;</li><li>Power on your Canon printer.&nbsp;</li><li>After that, check on the box - my device is set up and ready to be found.</li><li>Click on Next to complete the process.&nbsp;</li></ol>', '2023-08-03 06:59:12', '2023-08-03 06:59:12'),
(48, 4, 'How to Add a Bluetooth Canon Printer to Mac?', '<p>You must go through some simple steps to add a Bluetooth Canon printer to a Mac computer. Here are the steps.&nbsp;</p><ol><li>First of all, turn on your printer.&nbsp;</li><li>Connect your printer with Bluetooth by following the instructions in the user’s manual.&nbsp;</li><li>Tap on the Apple menu and navigate to System Settings.&nbsp;</li><li>Hit on Printers and Scanners.</li><li>Now, tap on Add a Printer, Scanner, or Fax button.&nbsp;</li><li>Later, click on the Default button.&nbsp;</li><li>Finally, select your printer from the printers list and tap on Add.&nbsp;</li></ol>', '2023-08-03 06:59:12', '2023-08-03 06:59:12'),
(49, 6, 'Why is My Epson Printer Not Connecting to Bluetooth on My Android Device?', '<p>Are you facing problems while operating your device with Bluetooth? You can try the solutions below and then try to connect the printer.&nbsp;</p><ol><li>First, confirm that the Bluetooth of your mobile phone is turned on.&nbsp;</li><li>Now, check if the Bluetooth light of your printer is flushing.</li><li>If the light is not pulling, try to pair the printer again.&nbsp;</li><li>Next, confirm that the printer is not communicating with another mobile device.&nbsp;</li><li>Make sure to disconnect the USB cable.</li></ol>', '2023-08-03 07:06:56', '2023-08-03 07:06:56'),
(50, 6, 'How to Enable Bluetooth Discovery Mode to Connect My iPhone to Epson Printer?', '<p>Epson Bluetooth printer setup can help you print from iPhone to Epson print using Bluetooth. Execute all the steps given below cautiously.&nbsp;</p><ol><li>Initiate by pressing the Power button. It is to turn off the printer.</li><li>Now, press the Power and Bluetooth buttons simultaneously.&nbsp;</li><li>The printer will power on, and the Bluetooth light will start pulsing.&nbsp;</li><li>Finally, pair your device to the Epson printer with instructions as per your device.&nbsp;</li></ol><p>Printer users can also seek the proper assistance from printer experts via calls or live chat. Simply visit our Support page and connect with them for a free consultation.&nbsp;</p>', '2023-08-03 07:06:56', '2023-08-03 07:06:56'),
(51, 6, 'How Can I Add a Bluetooth Printer to Mac?', '<p>Do you have a Bluetooth-installed printer? Read the instructions below to add a Bluetooth printer to your Mac device.&nbsp;</p><ol><li>Start with turning on your printer.&nbsp;</li><li>Go through the instructions to make your printer ready to connect.&nbsp;</li><li>Now, select the Apple menu and go to System Settings.&nbsp;</li><li>Tap on Add Printer, Scanner, or Fax button followed by Default.&nbsp;</li><li>Finally, select your printer from the list and hit on the Add option.&nbsp;</li></ol>', '2023-08-03 07:06:56', '2023-08-03 07:06:56'),
(52, 3, 'How to Print Through Bluetooth from an iPhone to an HP Printer?', '<p>You can easily print messages, photos, maps, and e-books from an iPhone to a printer. Bluetooth connectivity is the best option.&nbsp;</p><ol><li>Verify that your Bluetooth printer is discoverable.&nbsp;</li><li>Next, tap on Settings and then Bluetooth.&nbsp;</li><li>Slide the Bluetooth switch to ON.&nbsp;</li><li>Next, hit on your printer\'s name and connect it through Bluetooth.&nbsp;</li><li>Now, open the document/page you need to print.&nbsp;</li><li>Click on the curved arrow icon and open the pop-up menu.&nbsp;</li><li>Finally, tap on the Print option.&nbsp;</li></ol>', '2023-08-03 07:12:18', '2023-08-03 07:12:18'),
(53, 3, 'How Can I Troubleshoot Connection Problems with an HP Bluetooth Printer?', '<p>Bluetooth connectivity allows wireless printing, but sometimes there are some issues with the connection. In such a situation, you can follow the troubleshooting steps below.&nbsp;</p><ul><li>Confirm there is a proper proximity between the printer and your device.&nbsp;</li><li>Check your HP printer is compatible with Bluetooth connectivity.</li><li>Power off your printer and the device to solve temporary connection errors.&nbsp;</li><li>Install all the available updates.&nbsp;</li><li>Begin the pairing process from the start.</li><li>Make sure to turn off battery saving mode for optimal Bluetooth connection.&nbsp;</li></ul><p>Moreover, you can connect with printer experts for a free consultation. Visit our Support page and call or do a live chat to share your issues.&nbsp;</p>', '2023-08-03 07:12:18', '2023-08-03 07:12:18'),
(54, 3, 'How to Use Printer with Built-in Bluetooth for Wireless Printing?', '<p>Pair your printer with built-in bluetooth to print from a computer, mobile phone, or tablet. Here are some easy instructions for the process.&nbsp;</p><ol><li>Initially, turn on your printer\'s Bluetooth radio button.&nbsp;</li><li>The next step is to launch the Bluetooth Settings on your device.&nbsp;</li><li>Confirm the Bluetooth is turned on.&nbsp;</li><li>Now, select your printing device from the list of available devices.&nbsp;</li><li>After that, follow the steps to add your printer as a new device.&nbsp;</li><li>Open the item you need to print and then open the Print menu.&nbsp;</li><li>At last, choose your printer to begin printing.&nbsp;</li></ol><p>All these steps are easy to execute. But if you fail, don\'t forget to connect with a printer expert. You can visit our Support page and ask for a free consultation.&nbsp;</p>', '2023-08-03 07:12:18', '2023-08-03 07:12:18'),
(55, 7, 'Why is my Samsung printer not connecting to my computer?', '<p>If you are unable to perform the Samsung Bluetooth printer setup, then here are the key causes of that.&nbsp;</p><ul><li>The computer does not have permission to connect to your printer.&nbsp;</li><li>Computer and printer devices are not within the range.&nbsp;</li><li>Either printer or computer is having any technical issue.&nbsp;</li><li>The Samsung printer is missing the driver, or it does not have a compatible driver.&nbsp;</li><li>Your Samsung printer and PC are not compatible with each other.&nbsp;</li><li>The printer is not turned on properly, and many others.&nbsp;</li></ul>', '2023-08-03 07:21:20', '2023-08-03 07:21:20'),
(56, 7, 'How to set up a Samsung printer to a computer via Bluetooth?', '<p>Below are the steps you have to follow to set up a Samsung printer on a PC.&nbsp;</p><ol><li>First of all, download the compatible Samsung printer driver from HP’s support page.&nbsp;</li><li>After that, in your computer system, access the Printers and Devices window.&nbsp;</li><li>Next, make sure the Bluetooth is ON and then choose the Add Device option.&nbsp;</li><li>Now, from all the device options, you need to click on your Samsung printer name.&nbsp;</li><li>At the last steps, the printer setup will be complete.&nbsp;</li></ol>', '2023-08-03 07:21:20', '2023-08-03 07:21:20'),
(57, 7, 'How to set up a Samsung printer on a Mac device?', '<p>These steps will help you to set up a Samsung printer on a Mac.&nbsp;</p><ol><li>Begin by browsing the HP support page to download the driver.&nbsp;</li><li>After downloading the correct driver, install it on your Mac device.&nbsp;</li><li>Now, move to the Devices and Printers option after opening the System Preferences.&nbsp;</li><li>Next, click on the option of Add Device and move forward.&nbsp;</li><li>Then, select the printer and choose the appropriate option on the screen.&nbsp;</li><li>Finally, when things are done correctly, the Samsung printer setup will be complete.&nbsp;</li></ol>', '2023-08-03 07:21:20', '2023-08-03 07:21:20'),
(58, 8, 'How to connect a Xerox Bluetooth printer to a Windows computer?', '<p><font color=\"#0e101a\" face=\"Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.6667px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">The steps to connect the Xerox printer to a Windows device are as follows&nbsp;</span></font></p><ol><li><font color=\"#0e101a\" face=\"Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.6667px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">First, click the Start icon on the Taskbar and then select Settings.&nbsp;</span></font></li><li><font color=\"#0e101a\" face=\"Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.6667px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">In the settings, move to the Devices and Printers option.&nbsp;</span></font></li><li><font color=\"#0e101a\" face=\"Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.6667px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Choose the Add Printer option after making sure that Bluetooth is on.&nbsp;</span></font></li><li><font color=\"#0e101a\" face=\"Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.6667px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Now, look for your device in the result list and then click on it.&nbsp;</span></font></li><li><font color=\"#0e101a\" face=\"Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.6667px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">After that, the printer will connect to your Windows device.&nbsp;</span></font></li><li><font color=\"#0e101a\" face=\"Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.6667px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Once the connection is complete, install the driver to set up the printer.&nbsp;</span></font></li><li><font color=\"#0e101a\" face=\"Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.6667px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Lastly, the printer device will be ready to use.&nbsp;</span></font></li></ol>', '2023-08-03 07:27:38', '2023-08-03 07:27:38'),
(59, 8, 'How to connect a Xerox Bluetooth printer to a Mac?', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\">Here are the steps to connect the Xerox printer to a Mac device.&nbsp;</p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><ol><li style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">First, select the Apple menu and then choose the option of System Preferences.&nbsp;</li><li style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">After that, From the sidebar, click on Printers &amp; Scanners.&nbsp;</li><li style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Once that’s done, then move forward by choosing the Add Printer option.&nbsp;</li><li style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Now, you are required to select the Scanner or Fax button and then the Default option.&nbsp;</li><li style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Moreover, follow the on-display guide to complete the connection.&nbsp;</li><li style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Next, download and install the driver on your device. (You can also install the driver from CD.)</li><li style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Finally, print a test document to make sure the connection process is complete.&nbsp;</li></ol>', '2023-08-03 07:27:38', '2023-08-03 07:27:38'),
(60, 8, 'Why is my Xerox printer not connecting to a computer?', '<p>Some of the possible key causes of getting the issue of connecting the printer to the computer are as follows:</p><ul><li>The Xerox printer is missing the driver or does not have a genuine driver.&nbsp;</li><li>Computers and printers are not within the connection range.&nbsp;</li><li>Either printer or computer is having any technical issue.&nbsp;</li><li>Your printer is restricted from connecting to the computer you are trying to connect.</li><li>The printer and computer are not compatible with each other.&nbsp;</li><li>The printer is not turned on properly, and many others.&nbsp;</li></ul>', '2023-08-03 07:27:38', '2023-08-03 07:27:38');

